<br><br>
<font size="4" color="blue"><b>Kaur, H. and Raghava, G.P.S. (2003) BTEVAL: A server for evaluation of beta-turn prediction methods.<a href="http://www.worldscinet.com/jbcb/01/0103/S0219720003000253.html"> Journal of Bioinformatics and Computational Biology 3(1), 495-504.</a></b></font>

